THIRD-PARTY LICENSES

This project includes or uses the following open-source libraries:

1. Express.js (MIT)
   - Used for HTTP server in all backend services
   - https://expressjs.com/

2. GSAP (Standard License for Free Version)
   - Used for animations in UI
   - https://greensock.com/gsap/

3. TypeScript (Apache 2.0)
   - Used for type-safe development
   - https://www.typescriptlang.org/

4. Next.js (MIT)
   - Used for web interface
   - https://nextjs.org/

5. React (MIT)
   - Used as UI framework
   - https://react.dev/

6. Commander.js (MIT)
   - Used for CLI parsing
   - https://github.com/tj/commander.js

7. Chalk (MIT)
   - Used for CLI colors
   - https://github.com/chalk/chalk

8. UUID (MIT)
   - Used for unique ID generation
   - https://github.com/uuidjs/uuid

9. Axios (MIT)
   - Used for HTTP requests
   - https://axios-http.com/

10. Crypto (Node.js Built-in)
    - Used for encryption and hashing
    - https://nodejs.org/

